---
import Layout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">Last updated: 26/03/2026</p>

    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Pennine Digital (“I”, “me”, or “the studio”) is committed to respecting your privacy. This policy explains what personal information I
      collect, how it’s used, and your rights under UK GDPR.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-10 mb-4">1. Information I Collect</h2>

    <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">Contact Form</h3>
    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      When you send a message through my contact form, I collect your name, email address, and any information you include in your message.
      This information is processed by Netlify Forms and then forwarded directly to my Gmail inbox so I can reply to your enquiry. I do not
      store form submissions on this website.
    </p>

    <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2">Analytics</h3>
    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      This website uses Plausible Analytics, a privacy‑focused, cookie‑free analytics tool. Plausible collects non‑personal, aggregated data
      only, such as page views, referrers, and device type. No cookies are used, and no personal data is collected, stored, or shared.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-10 mb-4">2. How Your Information Is Used</h2>
    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      I use your information to respond to enquiries, provide quotes or project details, and communicate during a project. I do not sell or
      share your personal information with third parties for marketing.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-10 mb-4">3. How Your Information Is Stored</h2>
    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Contact form messages are stored in my Gmail inbox. Analytics data is anonymised and cannot identify you. No personal data is stored
      on this website’s server.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-10 mb-4">4. How Long Your Information Is Kept</h2>
    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Enquiry emails are kept for up to 12 months, or longer if we begin working together. You can request deletion at any time.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-10 mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Under UK GDPR, you have the right to access the personal data I hold about you, request corrections, request deletion, withdraw
      consent, and complain to the ICO if you believe your data has been mishandled. To exercise any of these rights, email me at: <strong
        >hello@penninedigital.co.uk</strong
      >.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-10 mb-4">6. Cookies</h2>
    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      This website does not use cookies for tracking or advertising. Plausible Analytics runs without cookies.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-10 mb-4">7. Third‑Party Services</h2>
    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">Your data may be processed by:</p>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      <li>Netlify (contact form processing)</li>
      <li>Gmail (email communication)</li>
      <li>Plausible Analytics (anonymous traffic insights)</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">These services process data on my behalf but do not use it for their own marketing.</p>

    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-10 mb-4">8. Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
      If you have any questions about this policy or how your data is handled, you can contact me at:
      <strong>hello@penninedigital.co.uk</strong>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
